Fabulous first time investment! You will not want to miss out!

Description:
Position And Convenience At Its Best.
Close at hand to all amenities and convenient in every aspect of the word, is this recently renovated apartment.
This residence boasts two bedrooms with built in robes, a lounge room, separate dining area, a spacious kitchen with plenty of storage space, bathroom with shower and bath, a separate toilet and a single car space.
This apartment would be a perfect buy for the first home buyers or investors looking to add to their portfolio in the ever growing Dandenong area. The property is currently tenanted and the tenants have expressed their intent to stay on.
Situated within walking distance to Dandenong Station, Dandenong Plaza Shopping centre and with the bus stop at the front of the building, this apartment will not last long.
Thinking of selling? Call us today; Boronia office on 9761 2277, Wantirna office on 9800 1225, Rowville office on 9755 6666 or Bayswater office on 9720 3030.
TO REGISTER YOUR INTEREST click on either of the following tabs and fill in your details, BOOK AN INSPECTION on the Biggin & Scott website or EMAIL AGENT / CONTACT AGENT on Real Estate.com.au and other websites. You will be contacted by one of our agents and will also receive a text advising of inspection times.

Description:
Executive Living!
Located in the highly sought after Metro Village Estate is this stunning two storey home. Upon entry you will be delighted with the open space in the front living area walking past the European laundry leading through to a downstairs powder room. There is a great sized open plan kitchen/living area with gas stainless steel appliances, glass splash back, stone bench tops and dishwasher. Complete with natural light is the well-appointed living area with double glass sliding doors
Upstairs you will find a study/3rd bedroom overlooking tranquil gardens, two large bedrooms with built in robes, master bedroom with direct access to a delightfully appointed bathroom featuring a double shower. With quality fixtures this property also boasts one of the largest courtyards on the street with side gate access as well as roller door access to a single remote lock up garage.
We have obtained all information above from sources we believe to be reliable; however, we cannot guarantee its accuracy. We do not accept any responsibility to any person for its accuracy and do no more than pass it on. All interested parties are advised to carry out their own investigations, and should make and rely upon their own enquiries in order to determine whether or not this information is in fact accurate.

Description:
** AUCTION THIS SATURDAY @ 11.30 AM **
An original home to renovate or rebuild (STCA)
It might be largely original, but for many, this home on around 533sqm is all about the position. And depending on your needs, this could be your first or next renovation, or maybe you could start again by designing and building the luxurious family home you've always dreamed of (STCA). In good condition, the home features polished hardwood floors throughout, a generous lounge with gas heater and an air conditioner plus a meals area adjoining the modern kitchen with stainless oven and cook top. There are 3 bedrooms that all feature built in wardrobes as well as a family bathroom, a dual entry toilet and a full laundry. Outside, the secure carport could accommodate up to 4 cars or serve double duty as a huge covered entertaining area while the backyard with garden shed is easy to maintain. And from here you can easily access buses, walking tracks and Eastlink with Dandenong train station, Dandenong South Primary School and all of central Dandenong's facilities just minutes away.
** Photo id required for all open for inspections **

Description:
Potential Plus In Central Locale!!!
LJ Hooker is proud to present this lovely Weatherboard home which is ideal for all First Home Buyers, astute investors and buyers looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after pocket of Dandenong. Sitting on 558m2 of prime soil approx. This home provides the convenient and ideal lifestyle you have been searching for.
For all investors out there this home is currently leased out to fantastic tenants for $1300PCM on a month to month basis. Retain the existing property and develop a second dwelling in the rear STCA or demolish and develop 2 large dwellings the choice is yours!
This home offers 3 good-sized bedrooms, a spacious lounge, dinning/meals area which is adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with gas cooking and an abundance of cupboard space. The main bathroom, toilet and separate laundry make up the interior of this wonderful home.
Features of this home include: ducted heating, air con, dishwasher, fireplace, separate bungalow with kitchenette and ensuite, a long driveway providing the option to add a garage or carport.
You are only within a short distance to Dandenong Plaza/ Market, Dandenong CBD Dandenong Train station, Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Hospital, Princess highway, freeway access, public transport, recreational facilities and so much more. This is the right choice for all!
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!

Description:
WHEN OLD BECOMES NEW
If you've been waiting for a home that is ready to move into with nothing else to do, then this is it. With fresh paint throughout, rejuvenated kitchen and bathroom, polished floorboards throughout and brand new floor tiles in the bathroom this home has been brought back to life and is ready for a new owner to show it the same love and care as before.
Each bedroom is complete with built in robes, there is both a shower and bath in the bathroom and you even get a separate laundry to accommodate your needs. With both heating and cooling in the lounge, external roller blinds and a private courtyard you can enjoy this home all year round.
Being only one of three on the block means you won't feel too cramped. This is the perfect start for a first home buyer, someone looking to downsize or the astute investor looking to add another property to their portfolio. Only minutes from all the amenities Dandenong has to offer this is the perfect position for those wanting to be within walking distance to the shops whilst maintaining a sense of quietness away from the bustle of the main thoroughfare.
